Fine.

102
00:10:21,350 --> 00:10:22,380
I'll get a part-time job.

103
00:10:23,150 --> 00:10:24,920
When I save enough money

104
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,320
to rent a place, I'll leave.

105
00:10:29,730 --> 00:10:30,480
What?

106
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:33,150
Nothing good happens when you look at me like this.

107
00:10:35,140 --> 00:10:36,350
You're overthinking it.

108
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:37,680
Puppy.

109
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:45,780
Don't touch me.

110
00:10:56,110 --> 00:10:58,300
Xinjia and I will handle the one who attacked us.

111
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,530
