115
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:08,410
Who?

116
00:11:18,190 --> 00:11:19,280
Honey.

117
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:20,770
Jessica.

118
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:21,600
You...

119
00:11:24,170 --> 00:11:25,230
Why are you here?

120
00:11:26,300 --> 00:11:27,250
I missed you.

121
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:30,650
It's just a joint investment mall project,

122
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:31,670
and it's been dragging on for so long.

123
00:11:32,140 --> 00:11:33,410
Your dad's really mad,

124
00:11:33,430 --> 00:11:34,780
so he asked me to come help.

125
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:41,970
What?

126
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:43,470
Don't you welcome me?

127
00:11:44,770 --> 00:11:45,720
No.

128
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:46,900
You came just in time.

129
00:11:46,940 --> 00:11:48,300
We were going to talk about this anyway.

130
00:11:49,100 --> 00:11:49,900
About what?

131
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,830
President, I heard that you sent Zheng Yunong to Taiwan to find Zixiang.

132
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:05,060
The progress in Taiwan has been too slow.

133
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:07,780
Plus, they are engaged.

134
00:12:07,810 --> 00:12:09,110
Being apart for too long isn't good either.

135
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:11,470
Let's see if working on the same thing

136
00:12:11,490 --> 00:12:13,530
will make their relationship better.

137
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:16,670
A family like us needs affection?

138
00:12:19,580 --> 00:12:24,020
Affection is the minimum connection we need.

139
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:27,980
Family interests always come first.

140
00:12:30,610 --> 00:12:33,450
I heard you've been getting close to Mr. Sun's granddaughter lately.

141
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:34,360
Yes.

142
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:36,370
For the family's benefit.

143
00:12:36,390 --> 00:12:37,190
Funny.

144
00:12:49,920 --> 00:12:51,450
Why did you pull me out here?

145
00:12:55,990 --> 00:12:58,410
To avoid that beautiful woman?

146
00:12:58,890 --> 00:13:00,510
What's her relationship with Yang Zixiang?

147
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:02,460
She walked in and immediately asked him to pour her tea.

148
00:13:02,930 --> 00:13:04,070
Do you think she's pretty?

149
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,090
I think she's alright.

150
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,130
Prettier than me?

151
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,680
Are you crazy?

152
00:13:12,130 --> 00:13:13,840
