166
00:13:43,940 --> 00:13:45,480
nor access my assets.

167
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:48,030
Let's just get married.

168
00:13:48,060 --> 00:13:49,600
After we marry, you can do whatever you want.

169
00:13:49,660 --> 00:13:50,730
I won't control you.

170
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:51,590
I swear

171
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:55,200
