177
00:14:08,870 --> 00:14:10,150
If he really likes you,

178
00:14:10,170 --> 00:14:11,270
tell him about this.

179
00:14:11,310 --> 00:14:12,300
He'll endure for you.

180
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:14,030
I don't know if he likes me.

181
00:14:14,340 --> 00:14:15,640
Even if he does,

182
00:14:16,050 --> 00:14:18,550
it's not a reason to ask him to endure for me.

183
00:14:19,380 --> 00:14:20,740
The person I like

184
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:24,360
has always been working hard to overcome his difficulties,

185
00:14:24,780 --> 00:14:26,150
chasing after his goals.

186
00:14:26,430 --> 00:14:29,170
[Xin'an Long-term Care Center]

187
00:14:30,940 --> 00:14:32,200
Mr. Jiang?

188
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,000
Hello.

189
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:34,790
Hello.

190
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:38,620
I'm the director of Xin'an.

191
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:42,250
Welcome to our team of caregivers at Xin'an.

192
00:14:42,460 --> 00:14:45,180
We've recently received a few patients who are deaf,

193
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:48,660
and we're looking for caregivers who understand them

194
00:14:48,690 --> 00:14:51,970
and have professional backgrounds.

195
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:54,630
Even if others doubt him,

196
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:56,020
saying it's impossible,

197
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,330
mock him,

198
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,390
and tell him he's dreaming,

199
00:14:59,670 --> 00:15:00,920
he didn't give up.

200
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,320
This way, please.

201
00:15:10,740 --> 00:15:12,960
He seizes every opportunity for an interview

202
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:15,670
and does his best in what he wants to do.

203
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:17,990
So, I'm ashamed of myself

204
00:15:18,070 --> 00:15:20,800
for being aimless and beating myself up.

205
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:24,360
Compared to him,

206
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:27,480
our troubles now seem

207
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:28,700
so indulgent.

208
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:31,290
To solve problems like this,

209
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:32,950
it feels pathetic.

210
00:15:35,850 --> 00:15:36,690
You really like him,

211
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:37,820
don't you?

212
00:15:40,260 --> 00:15:42,430
When I realized it, I already liked him a lot.

213
00:15:47,410 --> 00:15:48,560
You're so honest.

214
00:15:49,310 --> 00:15:50,540
What should I do?

215
00:15:56,220 --> 00:15:57,770
What are you trying to tell me?

216
00:15:58,920 --> 00:16:01,000
Find the person who wants to kill you with me.

217
00:16:05,590 --> 00:16:06,360
What?

218
00:16:06,380 --> 00:16:07,180
Scared?

219
00:16:08,090 --> 00:16:09,200
Who's scared?

220
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:10,880
He beat me up so badly.

221
00:16:10,910 --> 00:16:12,330
If I don't teach him a lesson,

222
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,660
I'd better change my name.

223
00:16:15,930 --> 00:16:16,570
Do you realize

224
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:19,000
this means you're going against Crazy Dog Dong?

225
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,350
Trying to leave the gang?

226
00:16:27,920 --> 00:16:28,850
I actually wasn't

227
00:16:30,110 --> 00:16:31,750
