228
00:16:32,940 --> 00:16:34,540
I made Brother Dong my boss...

229
00:16:35,460 --> 00:16:37,840
Without joining the gang, what's there to kill?

230
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:39,550
I just thought if I could achieve something,

231
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:41,080
I could become Brother Dong's right-hand man,

232
00:16:41,350 --> 00:16:42,620
with my own turf to manage.

233
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:46,200
I guess I was too simple-minded.

234
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:48,290
You're right.

235
00:16:49,570 --> 00:16:50,510
