236
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:52,750
But I have to settle the score for the beating.

237
00:16:53,210 --> 00:16:54,390
How do you want to catch him?

238
00:16:54,410 --> 00:16:55,140
I'll help you.

239
00:17:06,910 --> 00:17:07,920
I'm not a dog.

240
