250
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,940
I only found out because you said so.

251
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:00,090
Cut the crap.

252
00:18:00,410 --> 00:18:01,740
I don't have patience.

253
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:05,180
