267
00:19:43,340 --> 00:19:44,310
We can keep being friends.

268
00:19:44,330 --> 00:19:45,380
Why act like this?

269
00:19:52,870 --> 00:19:55,840
You have a fiancée but still say you like me.

270
00:19:55,860 --> 00:19:57,030
What's that about?

271
00:19:57,060 --> 00:19:58,300
How do you know?

272
00:20:02,130 --> 00:20:03,440
Let me explain.

273
00:20:21,790 --> 00:20:22,920
Auntie?

274
00:20:23,260 --> 00:20:24,430
Yes.

275
00:20:25,500 --> 00:20:26,300
Auntie.

276
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:28,340
Little Boss.

277
00:20:28,400 --> 00:20:30,620
Are you here to see Shaopeng again?

278
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:51,450
Where is Shaopeng?

279
00:20:56,210 --> 00:20:59,370
Why didn't you greet your guest but hid in your room instead?

280
00:21:03,240 --> 00:21:04,350
I'm sorry. Auntie.

281
00:21:05,130 --> 00:21:06,200
It's all my fault.

282
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,880
He's angry.

283
00:21:13,190 --> 00:21:15,630
I haven't seen him angry for a long time.

284
00:21:19,580 --> 00:21:21,310
All this time,

285
00:21:21,330 --> 00:21:24,070
he only lets us see him smile,

286
00:21:25,850 --> 00:21:27,550
never letting us worry.

